SIRT1 activation and its circadian clock control: a promising approach against 
(frailty in) neurodegenerative disorders.

Ribeiro RFN(1)(2)(3), Pereira D(1)(2), de Almeida LP(#)(4)(5)(6), Silva 
MMC(#)(7)(8)(9), Cavadas C(#)(10)(11)(12).

