The association between sociodemographic status and COPD and asthma mortality, 
DALY and YLD in southern China, 2005-2015.

Liao TT(1), Guan WJ(2), Zheng YJ(3), Wang Y(4), Xiao N(4), Li C(4), Xu YJ(4), He 
ZX(4), Meng RL(5), Zheng XY(6), Lin LF(7).

